These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: british, brazilian, nigerian, mexican
1. Nationality:brazilian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:mexican is between Nationality:british and Nationality:brazilian##2
3. Nationality:mexican is on the right of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | british | mexican | brazilian | nigerian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: pepper, pomegranate, peach, onion
1. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:onion##1
2. Food:pomegranate is in an odd position##4
3. Food:pomegranate is on the left or right of Food:pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pomegranate | pepper | onion | peach |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: action, romance, western, fantasy
1. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:action##3
2. Movie-Genre:action is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is between Movie-Genre:fantasy and Movie-Genre:romance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | fantasy | western | romance |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
