.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: raspberry, cauliflower, peas, kale
1. Food:cauliflower == Food:cauliflower##1
2. Food:kale is on the left or right of Food:peas##3
3. Food:peas is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:raspberry is in an even position##4
5. Food:kale is on the left of Food:cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | peas | kale | cauliflower | raspberry |

